    "body": "I compiled the `.c` program they provide in the link and ran the binary. Unfortunately it did not crash. They say the program should crash immediately if the kernel has the bug or it will run for 60 seconds if it's not vulnerable.\r\n\r\n```console\r\n$ time ./a.out\r\n0.00user 0.00system 1:00.01elapsed 0%CPU (0avgtext+0avgdata 1540maxresident)k\r\n0inputs+0outputs (0major+90minor)pagefaults 0swaps\r\n```\r\nThe kernel is in the version vulnerable error range but I don't know if it was compiled with GCC9 (vulnerable) or GCC8 (not vulnerable).\r\n\r\n```console\r\n$ uname -r\r\n5.3.0-42-generic\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n",
